 new immigration policy could let foreign criminals delay deportation — What we know]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131284030.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadas-new-immigration-policy-could-let-foreign-criminals-delay-deportation-what-we-know/articleshow/131284030.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canadas-new-immigration-policy-could-let-foreign-criminals-delay-deportation-what-we-know/articleshow/131284030.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T23:32:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131284339,imgsize-188278.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US, Iran move closer to 60-day ceasefire extension: What's in the deal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131282678.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The US and Iran are reportedly nearing a 60-day ceasefire extension, with mediators working on an interim deal. This agreement could pave the way for broader talks on Iran's nuclear program and regional security, including the gradual reopening of the Strait of Hormuz and phased sanctions relief for Tehran.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-iran-move-closer-to-60-day-ceasefire-extension-whats-in-the-deal/articleshow/131282678.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-iran-move-closer-to-60-day-ceasefire-extension-whats-in-the-deal/articleshow/131282678.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T21:57:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure ty