a.indiatimes.com/world/us/dont-mind-being-called-tyrant-dictator-but-dont-want-to-be-called-dumb-donald-trump/articleshow/131282090.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T21:36:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131282506,imgsize-830407.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin cancer specialist banned from practising in UK says, 'I will never work...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131280538.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/indian-origin-cancer-specialist-banned-from-practising-in-uk-says-i-will-never-work-in-that-country-again/articleshow/131280538.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/indian-origin-cancer-specialist-banned-from-practising-in-uk-says-i-will-never-work-in-that-country-again/articleshow/131280538.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T20:49:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131281885,imgsize-55890.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Hindus and Muslims teaming up to take over Texas': Jan 6 rioter's hate speech at Frisco council meeting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131281621.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hindus-and-muslims-teaming-up-to-take-over-texas-jan-6-rioters-hate-speech-at-frisco-council-meeting/articleshow/131281621.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hindus-and-muslims-teaming-up-to-take-over-texas-jan-6-rioters-hate-speech-at-frisco-council-meeting/articleshow/131281621.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T20:29:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131281684,imgsize-93176.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Pentagon releases footage of US jet shooting down mysterious UFO]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131281008.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Pentagon has released a new video showing a US fighter jet downing an unidentified object over Lake Huron in February 2023. This infrared footage, part of a declassified batch, depicts a "kinetic interaction" leading to the object's fragmentation. The release includes hundreds of files, documents, and videos related to "unidentified anomalous phenomena" (UAP), fueling public curiosity.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-pentagon-releases-video-showing-us-jet-taking-down-mysterious-object-in-second-tranche-of-ufo-files/articleshow/131281008.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-pentagon-releases-video-showing-us-jet-taking-down-mysterious-object-in-second-tranche-of-ufo-files/articleshow/131281008.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T19:44:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131280993,imgsize-4829028.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[DO NOT INVITE: Why Donald Trump offboarded Tulsi Gabbard]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131280699.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The gulf between Trump’s actions and Gabbard’s worldview made the latter’s position untenable. Perhaps her fate was sealed last June when, less than two weeks before Operation Midnight Hammer, she posted a video in which she said “political elite warmongers are carelessly fomenting fear and tensions between nuclear powers”. The post appeared shortly before the US struck Iran’s nuclear sites in an operation almost borrowed from the plot of Top Gun: Maverick.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/do-not-invite-why-donald-trump-offboarded-tulsi-gabbard/articleshow/131280699.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/do-not-invite-why-donald-trump-offboarded-tulsi-gabbard/articleshow/131280699.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T19:43:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Nirmalya Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131280697,imgsize-118450.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin worker killed by falling branch in NZ, wife left 'completely alone']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131280337.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-worker-killed-by-falling-branch-in-new-zealand-wife-left-completely-alone-without-money/articleshow/131280337.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-origin-worker-killed-by-falling-branch-in-new-zealand-wife-left-completely-alone-without-money/articleshow/131280337.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T19:05:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131280467,imgsize-69588.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian national charged after alleged $5.6m pseudoephedrine import bust at Sydney port]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace