tating fire at a New York City shipyard ignited two powerful explosions, claiming one life and injuring at least 36, including brave firefighters and first responders.  The "complex, fast-developing emergency" saw crews battling flames late into the night after the blasts rocked the area. Investigations into the cause are underway.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fast-developing-emergency-1-killed-several-injured-after-fire-explosions-at-new-york-city-shipyard/articleshow/131278170.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fast-developing-emergency-1-killed-several-injured-after-fire-explosions-at-new-york-city-shipyard/articleshow/131278170.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T16:45:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131278341,imgsize-634314.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Uganda confirms 3 new Ebola cases as WHO warns against underestimating outbreak risk]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131277784.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Uganda has confirmed three new Ebola cases, bringing the total to five in the current outbreak. The new infections include a driver and a health worker exposed to the first patient, along with a woman from the Democratic Republic of Congo. Authorities are intensifying contact tracing efforts to contain the spread of the rare Bundibugyo strain.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/uganda-confirms-3-new-ebola-cases-as-who-warns-against-underestimating-outbreak-risk/articleshow/131277784.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/uganda-confirms-3-new-ebola-cases-as-who-warns-against-underestimating-outbreak-risk/articleshow/131277784.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-23T16:08:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131277799,imgsize-1297255.cms"/></item></channel></rss>